{
  "stem": "214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was August, and came-- no, September was quiet, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was those-- those plans were done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we are going to go there and wait until-- I don't know what-- until doomsday?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- you know, then some people found out about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were more and more people being, you know-- wanted to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then through the month of September, nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no deportation until October 3rd.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Deportation took place.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And most of the people in the town were taken away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that we were there all this time, and my sister and I, we would walk out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or sometimes we would, you know, travel to sell-- I don't know what-- a bracelet, a ring, maybe, if there was something left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and then, yeah, now I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While the deportation took place on the 3rd of October, I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because after the first deportation, a friend of mine, [NON-ENGLISH], she-- she, again, started, you know, we should-- we should start work-- we should work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now they changed the color of the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, the Germans need the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we joined one of those work groups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were driving out every morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was also on-- with trucks-- I don't know, about 12, 15 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember-- and digging something again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we were working on the field.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, when we were at work, and my sister was away-- I don't know where she was-- you know, again, traveling to smuggle something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we heard rumors about 11 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was also an interesting incident.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
